  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I called her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She didn't know who I was because she tried to look for me too.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And a lot of people gave her a different leads, bad leads.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So naturally, we-- we found out that we are sisters and brothers because then a couple of months later, a month later I think, she decide and came to Newark to visit me.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that's-- we had our reunion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was all over in the newspaper that brother found his sister after 20 years.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And later on, we decide [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to move to Las Vegas, that I should be closer to-- to my sister.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister never-- didn't have any children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We came to Las Vegas in 1962.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The first time we came in 1960 for a visit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we decided to move to Las Vegas in 1962.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's where we moved, to Las Vegas 1962.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I-- my brother-in-law was in business, and he gave me offer to become a partner in his business.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I took him on the offer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And here-- and I become a-- a jeweler.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, most important of me right now is my family because I-- [DRINKS] I went through so much.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I seen a lot of families during the war being torn apart, killed, and that's-- my family is my-- most important.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Looking back at my life, I was-- I had like a-- three full lives because my life was divided in the different-- different sections, or different plateaus, or-- or different-- I remember my childhood.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was my part one part.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Later, the war.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After that was part of my life, and later on, meeting my sister, there was another section-- part of my life.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And now, thank God, I-- I'm OK.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm healthy, and maybe comfortable, and having my family together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm married 49 years.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have one daughter, and I have two lovely grandchildren.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And a son-in-law.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
